    "risaa_customer_reviews": {
      "type": "risaa-customer-reviews",
      "blocks": {
        "rev_1": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "review_text": "Risaa Design Studio is my go-to place whenever I need an outfit for any occasion! Ms. Rima and her design team created beautiful ensembles for both my roka and CA convocation ceremony. She always brings my vision to life in an even more elegant way, ensuring that every outfit fits me perfectly and complements me beautifully. I have never received any of my outfits later than the timeline initially promised, and every piece has fit like a glove from the very first trial itself.",
            "reviewer_name": "Pallavi Oberoi",
            "reviewer_meta": "New Delhi",
            "show_verified": true
          }
        },
        "rev_2": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "review_text": "Had the best experience at Risaa during my two trips. RiSaa was introduced to me by my dear friend Aman, who is a regular visitor to RiSaa. I had lehengas designed for both my daughter and daughter-in-law, and both were stunning. I also had a long gown made for my son's wedding reception, which Rima and her team created to perfection. Thanks, Risaa, for getting everything ready on time, and best wishes for your venture to grow and expand even more!",
            "reviewer_name": "",
            "reviewer_meta": "",
            "show_verified": true
          }
        },
        "rev_3": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "review_text": "I loved the complete makeover of my saree into a beautiful customised lehenga, loved the patchwork, choli, dupatta and the whole outfit! Thanks to Rima and the whole team of Risaa for their efforts and for designing my outfit gracefully!",
            "reviewer_name": "",
            "reviewer_meta": "",
            "show_verified": true
          }
        },
        "rev_4": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "review_text": "Thank you so much for making my amazing wedding lehenga and engagement lehenga. Everyone just loved it!",
            "reviewer_name": "",
            "reviewer_meta": "",
            "show_verified": true
          }
        },
        "rev_5": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "review_text": "My customised bridal outfit was so beautiful that, to this day, everyone asks me where I got it designed and made. All the compliments I received and my amazing look were courtesy of Risaa. Thank you so much for the lovely design and the incredible support throughout the process!",
            "reviewer_name": "",
            "reviewer_meta": "",
            "show_verified": true
          }
        },
        "rev_6": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "review_text": "I just wanted to say thank you so much for getting all of my suits ready in the short time frame I had. I really, really appreciate it. The parrot green suit is done so very beautifully. Literally everyone I show it to is in love with the work done on the salwar. And the potli matching the other suit is so cute! Can't wait to order from you again! Thank you once again!",
            "reviewer_name": "",
            "reviewer_meta": "",
            "show_verified": true
          }
        },
        "rev_7": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "review_text": "Thanks for the beautiful dress! Everyone praised it a lot. In fact, everyone praised all the pre-wedding outfits I got custom-made from you, my pre-wedding shoot outfit, Haldi outfit, and bachelorette dress! You truly made my day. Thanks!",
            "reviewer_name": "",
            "reviewer_meta": "",
            "show_verified": true
          }
        },
        "rev_8": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "review_text": "Thanks for the beautiful kaftan dress, I just loved it. Love the co-ord set I got from you too. It looked beautiful. Thank you so much!",
            "reviewer_name": "Shagun Jindal",
            "reviewer_meta": "Ludhiana",
            "show_verified": true
          }
        },
        "rev_9": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "review_text": "Absolutely loved the custom suit - elegant and perfect! Thank you so much for such great work!",
            "reviewer_name": "",
            "reviewer_meta": "",
            "show_verified": true
          }
        },
        "rev_10": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "review_text": "My kaftan is mind-blowing, and so was my suit! Both outfits were beautiful, and the embroidery was too good. The fitting of both was perfect too. Thanks a lot!",
            "reviewer_name": "",
            "reviewer_meta": "",
            "show_verified": true
          }
        },
        "rev_11": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "review_text": "Perfect fit! I was amazed at how perfectly the dress fit me despite ordering it from Dubai. I was sceptical about how we would manage without trials due to the distance, but the dress fit me perfectly in one go!",
            "reviewer_name": "",
            "reviewer_meta": "",
            "show_verified": true
          }
        },
        "rev_12": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "review_text": "I got my parcel today, and the dress is amazing! The fitting and everything else are amazing. It's just wow! Thanks to Risaa!",
            "reviewer_name": "",
            "reviewer_meta": "",
            "show_verified": true
          }
        }
      },
